alue":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>orientationchange</code> 事件在設備方向改變時被觸發。</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>冒泡</th>\n      <th>No</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>可取消</td>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>介面</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>事件處理器</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/onorientationchange\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>onorientationchange</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>可於 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener</code></a> 方法中使用 <code>abort</code> 事件：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"orientationchange\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"the orientation of the device is now \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>orientation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>angle<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>或使用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/onorientationchange\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>onorientationchange</code></a> 事件處理器屬性：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onorientationchange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"the orientation of the device is now \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>orientation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>angle<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://compat.spec.whatwg.org/#event-orientationchange","title":"Compatibility Standard"}],"query":"api.Window.orientationchange_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Window.orientationchange_event","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Window/orientationchange_event/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"}],"summary":"orientationchange 事件在設備方向改變時被觸發。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window: orientationchange event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window: orientationchange イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"orientationchange","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"orientationchange","locale":"z